node.title: Waitematā Harbour training exercise keeps rescue chopper busy
node.description: A seemingly dramatic rescue is under way on Auckland's Waitematā Harbour, but it's not what it seems.
node.content:
["A seemingly dramatic rescue is under way on Auckland's Waitematā Harbour, but it's not what it seems.", "", "
A training exercise on the Waitematā Harbour Photo: Supplied
", "A crew member has been seen being winched from the rescue helicopter onto a yacht off Beach Haven.", "The chopper then escorted the boat down the harbour.", "However, the Auckland Rescue Helicopter Trust says it's part of a winching training exercise with the Coastguard.", "The helicopter will be active over the next two days in the Upper Harbour and Brown's Island area."]
